1300
01:14:59,833 --> 01:15:01,400
Oh, yeah.

1301
01:15:01,433 --> 01:15:03,400
Oh, it must have been
awful for them.

1302
01:15:03,433 --> 01:15:06,133
But you know, little Steven
was severely injured.

1303
01:15:06,167 --> 01:15:08,567
They just didn't have the money
to pay for those operations.

1304
01:15:09,967 --> 01:15:11,700
Let me see
if I can find that file.

1305
01:15:15,467 --> 01:15:16,967
Marge: Olivia Jordan's office.

1306
01:15:17,067 --> 01:15:18,200
Marge, it's Max.

1307
01:15:18,233 --> 01:15:20,100
Has Olivia gotten back
to the office yet?

1308
01:15:20,133 --> 01:15:21,933
No, not yet.

1309
01:15:21,967 --> 01:15:23,333
Has she called in?

1310
01:15:23,367 --> 01:15:25,767
No. I should be hearing 
 from her soon.

1311
01:15:26,800 --> 01:15:28,067
Thanks, Marge.

1312
01:15:28,067 --> 01:15:29,367
(bleeps)

1313
01:15:34,700 --> 01:15:36,067
Ah, Jordan.

1314
01:15:37,733 --> 01:15:38,900
Wait.

1315
01:15:40,067 --> 01:15:41,167
It isn't here.

1316
01:15:42,200 --> 01:15:44,333
I've never lost a file.
I can't believe it.

1317
01:15:44,367 --> 01:15:45,867
Oh, no...

1318
01:15:45,900 --> 01:15:47,500
That's the strangest thing.

1319
01:15:49,400 --> 01:15:51,200
You may want to try
the welfare office.

1320
01:15:51,233 --> 01:15:52,500
You know,
little Steven was placed

1321
01:15:52,533 --> 01:15:54,067
in several foster homes.

1322
01:15:54,067 --> 01:15:55,900
