1325
01:16:04,533 --> 01:16:05,867
(dials number)

1326
01:16:08,667 --> 01:16:13,933
(phone ringing)

1327
01:16:19,567 --> 01:16:20,667
(exhales)

1328
01:16:25,933 --> 01:16:27,233
This is so weird.

1329
01:16:27,267 --> 01:16:29,133
The entire file is missing.

1330
01:16:29,167 --> 01:16:30,533
Fingerprints,
last known address,

1331
01:16:30,567 --> 01:16:32,800
the whole bit.
I don't know...

1332
01:16:32,833 --> 01:16:35,067
Okay, um, is...
is there any way that I can

1333
01:16:35,100 --> 01:16:37,667
-speak to the Johnsons?
-Yeah, sure.

1334
01:16:37,700 --> 01:16:39,267
I know the wife.
The Johnsons

1335
