have taken a lot of kids in
over the years.

1336
01:16:41,867 --> 01:16:43,067
Wait a second...

1337
01:16:44,533 --> 01:16:46,067
I don't believe it!

1338
01:16:46,100 --> 01:16:47,233
It's not here!

1339
01:16:48,267 --> 01:16:49,300
Oh, wait.

1340
01:16:50,633 --> 01:16:52,367
I have it in my address book.

1341
01:16:53,133 --> 01:16:54,433
Johnson. Here it is.

1342
01:16:56,400 --> 01:16:57,833
Thank you very much.

1343
01:17:04,567 --> 01:17:05,567
(bleeps)

1344
01:17:08,233 --> 01:17:09,767
Hi, Marge. Did Max call?

1345
01:17:09,800 --> 01:17:11,467
He was here looking for you.

1346
01:17:11,500 --> 01:17:14,067
I didn't know what to tell him.
I said you were at the bank...

1347
01:17:14,100 --> 01:17:15,367
Hope that's okay.

1348
01:17:15,400 --> 01:17:16,433
Okay.

1349
01:17:16,467 --> 01:17:18,467
Thanks. Yeah,
I'll talk to you later.

1350
01:17:18,500 --> 01:17:19,500
Bye.

1351
01:17:25,467 --> 01:17:26,433
Olivia...?!

1352
01:17:32,600 --> 01:17:34,367
-Olivia!
-(clattering)

1353
01:17:46,333 --> 01:17:47,600
Mrs. Johnson?

1354
01:17:47,633 --> 01:17:50,267
Are you the woman the
welfare worker called about?

1355
01:17:50,300 --> 01:17:51,567
I'm Olivia Jordan.

1356
01:17:52,433 --> 01:17:54,267
I'm looking for Steven Jordan.

1357
01:17:54,300 --> 01:17:57,133
I haven't seen that boy
in 15 years or better...

1358
01:17:57,167 --> 01:17:58,467
not that I've tired looking.

1359
01:17:59,533 --> 01:18:01,700
