I swear to you, it's me.

1511
01:28:37,200 --> 01:28:38,267
He set this up!

1512
01:28:38,300 --> 01:28:39,533
Stay away from me!

1513
01:28:43,300 --> 01:28:46,100
Olivia, our honeymoon in Venice,

1514
