1516
01:28:49,200 --> 01:28:50,600
And we bought
those funny shirts.

1517
01:28:50,633 --> 01:28:51,700
Stop!

1518
01:28:51,733 --> 01:28:53,433
And we rented that car
and we drove out

1519
01:28:53,467 --> 01:28:55,567
to the countryside and
I bought you those roses.

1520
01:28:55,600 --> 01:28:57,300
-Just stop it!
-Do you remember the roses?

1521
01:28:57,333 --> 01:29:00,367
What we did with the roses?
We made love...

1522
01:29:01,900 --> 01:29:04,433
We made love on a bed of roses.

1523
01:29:35,300 --> 01:29:38,100
(struggling)

1524
01:30:03,967 --> 01:30:06,500
No!

1525
01:30:06,533 --> 01:30:07,533
(gunshot)

1526
01:30:08,200 --> 01:30:09,767
Male voice: Olivia!

1527
01:30:28,133 --> 01:30:29,367
Man: Champagne for everyone.

1528
01:30:29,400 --> 01:30:31,133
Here we are. Here we go.

1529
01:30:31,167 --> 01:30:32,533
No, no, no.
Orange juice for me.

1530
01:30:32,567 --> 01:30:33,800
-Oh, that's right.
-What are you thinking?

1531
01:30:33,833 --> 01:30:34,900
-Huh?
-You tried to poison

1532
01:30:34,933 --> 01:30:35,967
-our Godchild?
-This is my baby, here.

1533
01:30:36,000 --> 01:30:37,033
She's gotta have her vitamins...

1534
01:30:37,067 --> 01:30:38,567
There we go.
Let's have a toast

1535
01:30:38,600 --> 01:30:40,300
to a successful venture.

1536
01:30:40,333 --> 01:30:41,733
Hear, hear.

1537
01:30:41,767 --> 01:30:44,100
I'd like to make
a special toast if I could.

1538
01:30:44,133 --> 01:30:45,833
To good fortune...

1539
01:30:47,267 --> 01:30:48,400
...to good friends...

1540
01:30:51,667 --> 01:30:54,033
...and to the family
I never thought that I'd have.

1541
01:30:54,067 --> 01:30:55,100
(gushes)

